                <li><a href="/Laptops"><img src="https://store.storeimages.cdn-apple.com/4668/as-images.apple.com/is/store-card-13-mac-nav-202310?wid=400&hei=260&fmt=png-alpha&.v=1696964122666" alt="Laptops"> Laptops & Tablets</a></li>
